OL,3,CNo plans for King and Queen to meet
OL,4,CEpstein survivors in US
OL,6,FThere are no plans for the King and
OL,7,FQueen to meet any survivors and
OL,8,Fvictims of the paedophile Jeffrey
OL,9,FEpstein when they are on US soil at
OL,10,Fthe end of April.
OL,12,FITV News understands that the ongoing
OL,13,Fpolice investigation into the King's
OL,14,Fbrother, Andrew Mountbatten-Windsor,
OL,15,Fwill prevent any such meeting from
OL,16,Ftaking place.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
