OL,3,CNo plans for King and Queen to meet
OL,4,CEpstein survivors in US
OL,6,FA US lawmaker has urged King Charles
OL,7,Fto come face to face with the victims
OL,8,Fof Epstein, during the four-day State
OL,9,FVisit which has now been confirmed by
OL,10,Fboth Buckingham Palace and the White
OL,11,FHouse.
OL,13,FCongressman Ro Khanna, a Democrat who
OL,14,Frepresents California in the lower
OL,15,Fhouse of Congress, helped to convince
OL,16,Fthe US Justice Department to release
OL,17,Fthe millions of Epstein and make them
OL,18,Favailable to the public.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
