OL,3,CNo plans for King and Queen to meet
OL,4,CEpstein survivors in US
OL,6,FHe had asked the King and Queen to
OL,7,Fmeet privately with survivors and
OL,8,Fcampaigners.
OL,10,FHowever, following the arrest of
OL,11,FAndrew Mountbatten-Windsor and the
OL,12,Fongoing criminal investigation by
OL,13,FThames Valley Police into the offence
OL,14,Fof misconduct in public office, palace
OL,15,Fsources suggest any meeting with
OL,16,FEpstein victims would risk prejudicing
OL,17,Fthose inquiries.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
