OL,3,CNo plans for King and Queen to meet
OL,4,CEpstein survivors in US
OL,6,FPreviously, the King and Queen have
OL,7,Fsaid their "sympathies have been, and
OL,8,Fremain with, the victims of any and
OL,9,Fall forms of abuse" and palace aides
OL,10,Fpoint to Queen Camilla's longstanding
OL,11,Fsupport for charities which support
OL,12,Fvictims of domestic violence and abuse.
OL,14,FCongressman Khan wrote in a letter to
OL,15,FKing Charles that "Epstein's network
OL,16,Fhad significant ties to the United
OL,17,FKingdom through Ghislaine Maxwell" and
OL,18,Fthose connections "raise broader
OL,19,Fquestions about how Epstein was able
OL,20,Fto maintain influence, credibility and
OL,21,Fprotection across borders for so long."
