OL,3,CNo plans for King and Queen to meet
OL,4,CEpstein survivors in US
OL,6,FLawmakers in the US have previously
OL,7,Fsought testimony from Mr Mountbatten-
OL,8,FWindsor.
OL,10,FThis is the first time the King has
OL,11,Fbeen to the United States since the
OL,12,FEpstein scandal exposed the extent and
OL,13,Fduration of his younger brother's
OL,14,Frelationship with Epstein.
OL,16,FCharles stripped Andrew of his
OL,17,Fdukedom, his prince title and his
OL,18,Fhouse in Windsor last year, saying he
OL,19,Fhad shown many "errors of judgement".
